687
00:55:41,000 --> 00:55:43,753
Well, you're every bit as attraactive
as David said you were

688
00:55:43,880 --> 00:55:45,677
I'm sure he's never
stopped talking about me.

689
00:55:49,240 --> 00:55:53,392
- Surprise.
